          <a class="btn02 category" href="/ko/taxonomy/term/4">에세이</a>
        </div>
        <h1>할머니의 방 -이옥선 할머니 편-</h1>
        <div class="writers">
          <p><b>글</b>
                      <b>김대월</b><em>나눔의집 학예실장 </em>
                    </p>
        </div>
        <ul class="metas">
          <li><b>게시일</b><span>2020.07.22</span></li>
          <li><b>최종수정일</b><span>2022.01.25</span></li>
        </ul>
        <div class="ng03">
          <a href="#" class="share" title="공유하기"><i class="xi-share-alt-o"></i></a>
